OL,3,C'Time is short' as talks to save
OL,4,CDerby's Alstom train factory continue
OL,6,FA major train manufacturer in Derby is
OL,7,Fwarning that "time is short" as talks
OL,8,Fcontinue with the Government to
OL,9,Fprovide enough work for its plant to
OL,10,Fremain open.
OL,12,F, which took over the 180-year-old
OL,13,FBombardier firm in 2021, has warned
OL,14,Fthat it will have to close the
OL,15,Ffactory, cutting all 3,000 jobs at the
OL,16,FLitchurch Lane site, if it can't
OL,17,Fsecure new train orders for work
OL,18,Fbeyond May this year.
