OL,3,C'Time is short' as talks to save
OL,4,CDerby's Alstom train factory continue
OL,6,FWith the cancellation of the northern
OL,7,Fleg of HS2, and delays to the project
OL,8,Foverall, Alstom bosses say there's a
OL,9,Fgap in productivity for the site which
OL,10,Fwill mean it's not viable to keep it
OL,11,Fopen, and work will be moved overseas.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
