OL,3,C'Time is short' as talks to save
OL,4,CDerby's Alstom train factory continue
OL,6,FSpeaking to BBC Radio 4, Nick
OL,7,FCrossfield, Alstom's UK Managing
OL,8,FDirector said; "We're coming to the
OL,9,Fend of a very large programme that
OL,10,Fwe've delivered over the past four
OL,11,Fyears. New build is in the process of
OL,12,Fending right now. Between now and May-
OL,13,FJune time, we will effectively go down
OL,14,Fto a position where there is very
OL,15,Flittle or no activity in what is one
OL,16,Fof the group's largest facilities
OL,17,Fworldwide.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
