OL,3,C'Time is short' as talks to save
OL,4,CDerby's Alstom train factory continue
OL,6,F"We've been in discussions with the
OL,7,FGovernment now for around 10 to 11
OL,8,Fmonths and we've been exploring with
OL,9,Fthe Government the possibility of
OL,10,Fbringing work into the facility for
OL,11,Fthe next 18 months. The market is
OL,12,Fthere in the medium to long term. What
OL,13,Fwe're talking about is covering a gap
OL,14,Fof around 18 to 19 months.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
