OL,3,C'Time is short' as talks to save
OL,4,CDerby's Alstom train factory continue
OL,6,F"We've been talking to the Government
OL,7,Fspecifically about accelerating future
OL,8,Fprojects and refurbishment projects
OL,9,Finto the facility that would allow us
OL,10,Fto maintain that capability, and when
OL,11,Fthe market comes back and the volume
OL,12,Fstarts to return, we can re-mobilise.
OL,13,FBut we've been at this now for 11
OL,14,Fmonths and we're here at this point in
OL,15,Ftime with no firm commitment.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
