OL,3,C'Time is short' as talks to save
OL,4,CDerby's Alstom train factory continue
OL,6,F"As we sit today, we don't have enough
OL,7,Fof a commitment to guarantee that we
OL,8,Fwill maintain a presence in the UK, at
OL,9,FDerby. We've got some very specific
OL,10,Fproposals which we've suggested to the
OL,11,FGovernment that would work for us. But
OL,12,Fwe do need a decision, we need a clear
OL,13,Fcommitment that this volume will come.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
