OL,3,C'Time is short' as talks to save
OL,4,CDerby's Alstom train factory continue
OL,6,F"They've been collaborative
OL,7,Fdiscussions, they've been very
OL,8,Fdetailed discussions. We've provided
OL,9,Fthe Government with a great degree of
OL,10,Finformation and the rationale for why
OL,11,Fit makes sense to do these things. But
OL,12,Funfortunately we are here with no
OL,13,Fdecision. It's a straight business
OL,14,Fdecision, we do not have, today, the
OL,15,Fcommitment that would allow us to take
OL,16,Fthe decision to remain."
OL,18,FHe added that the company is competing
OL,19,Ffor contracts globally, but that the
OL,20,Fsize of the facility at Derby needs a
OL,21,Fmixture of contracts to work on.
