OL,3,C'Time is short' as talks to save
OL,4,CDerby's Alstom train factory continue
OL,6,FThere are 3,000 jobs currently at the
OL,7,Fplant, which supports a further 12,000-
OL,8,F15,000 in the national supply chain.
OL,10,FMr Crossfield said; "Ultimately the
OL,11,Fwhole 3,000 is at risk, and the impact
OL,12,Fon the supply chain would be
OL,13,Fconsiderable."
OL,15,FIn a statement to ITV News, the
OL,16,Fcompany said; "Adessia will be
OL,17,FAlstom's next generation of commuter
OL,18,Ftrain, and it is a huge opportunity
OL,19,Ffor Derby and the wider UK rail sector.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
