OL,3,C'Time is short' as talks to save
OL,4,CDerby's Alstom train factory continue
OL,6,F"We are continuing to hold very
OL,7,Fconstructive discussions with the
OL,8,FDepartment for Transport to find a
OL,9,Fsustainable future for Derby, but time
OL,10,Fis short as our current projects are
OL,11,Falmost complete.
OL,13,F"We are committed to working with the
OL,14,FGovernment to create the certainty our
OL,15,Fstaff and UK suppliers need and
OL,16,Fdeserve."
